self-admiration as a political act.
self-celebration as a political act.
flaunting myself as a political act.

gazing in the mirror & unabashedly admiring my beauty, my softness, my melanin, my body in its reflection, during a time when I’m “supposed” to shrink myself & be modest as a political act.
• • •
this moment of feeling myself brought to you by Mercury going direct, this new moon in Aries, & Oshun. 🍯
#radicalselflove #femalegaze #unashamed #mybodyisnotanapology #oshun #sensuality #mirrorwork #blackgirlmagic

@cusp_kid this is not a waste of time but a bold declaration that says you are here, you deserve to be here, & that your body (& the admiration of it) is OK to be celebrated. i’m rooting for you, babe. 💖💖💖
